headline: Dollar Tree earnings, Fed president commentary: What to Watch
summary: Market Domination Overtime hosts Julie Hyman and Josh Lipton break down what to watch on Wednesday, March 26. Chewy (CHWY), Cintas (CTAS), Dollar Tree (DLTR), Paychex (PAYX), and Petco (WOOF) are all reporting quarterly earnings results. Additionally, Federal Reserve Bank of Minneapolis president Neel Kashkari and Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis president Alberto Musalem will be providing Fed commentary. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime here.
